      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric per ASME V&V 40 Section 8. E/uval = 1.31 for stiffness, 0.87 for yield force, 1.44 for force at 40 mm. All values below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences: stiffness 4.2%, yield force 3.1%, force at 40 mm 6.8% — all within 10% acceptance bound."
