    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test Conditions factor being below required level (achieved 1, required 2). The shortfall is offset by strong performance across all other 12 factors, with E/uval values well below 1.96 for all three QoIs and independent two-laboratory corroboration. The single-condition limitation is documented and accepted by the regulatory submission team as consistent with the scope of the 510(k) predicate comparison.",
